8308465: Reduce memory reads in AArch64 MD5 intrinsic

The performance is improved by ~ with `micro:org.openjdk.bench.java.security.MessageDigests`.

|------------|---------|--------|--------------|---------------|-------|
|            | 64      | 16,384 | 64           | 16,384        | bytes |
| Graviton 2 | -1.37%  | 1.51%  | -0.65%       | 1.89%         |
